{"type":"message","id":"a9d93823","parentId":"fbd82da0","timestamp":"2026-03-18T17:16:51.500Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"技能市场还在加载中。让我给用户一个回复，说明我理解了，并且愿意去安装新的技能来扩宽信息来源。","thinkingSignature":"aed3323dae2ea4517c35e2b79b608e41482a547e302ee8ed18d238fb6fb4c87c"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！🛡️\n\n明白了，ClawHub 是 OpenClaw 的技能市场，可以通过 `px clawhub@latest install <skill>` 安装新技能。\n\n目前我只加载了飞书相关的技能。你可以给我一些方向，比如：\n\n1. **搜索能力** - 想装一个更强的搜索技能？\n2. **数据处理** - 如 Excel、数据库相关？\n3. **知识管理** - 如 Notion、Obsidian 集成？\n4. **生产力工具** - 如 Linear、Jira、Trello？\n5. **其他** - 你希望我具备什么新能力？\n\n或者你推荐几个有用的技能名称，我自己去探索安装？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2720,"output":160,"cacheRead":38232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41112,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773854192012}}
