{"type":"message","id":"e36bc043","parentId":"2d63719a","timestamp":"2026-03-18T17:20:21.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好多彩！让我挑选一些对 Agent 管理员有用的：\n\n1. **session-logs** - 查看会话日志，对排查问题很有用\n2. **cron-manager** - 定时任务管理（我已经有了一个简化版）\n3. **model-usage** - 查看模型使用情况\n4. **github** - GitHub 操作\n5. **healthcheck** - 我已经有了\n\n让我先安装 **session-logs** 技能，这样可以查看会话日志来排查问题。","thinkingSignature":"8385bf0763944befac9a6fb22c3e4d2c54828c46f620901a149e5c78f46467a9"},{"type":"text","text":"好多彩！让我挑几个有用的：\n\n- **session-logs** - 查看会话日志，排查问题\n- **model-usage** - 查看模型使用情况\n- **github** - GitHub 操作\n\n先安装 **session-logs**，这对排查 Agent 问题很有帮助：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ng4jzynmwmeq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-ChildItem 'C:\\Users\\16343\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\ClawX\\resources\\openclaw\\skills\\session-logs' | Select-Object Name\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":7194,"output":220,"cacheRead":38232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45646,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773854416769}}
